Document: StyleBoxEmpty
Path: godot/classes/class_styleboxempty.rst
Summary: An empty StyleBox that can be used to display nothing instead of the default style, allowing for the disabling of focus styles.

An empty StyleBox that can be used to display nothing instead of the default style (e.g. it can "disable" focus styles).